    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236710/extras/5d988c72aa3ab92995f295a389808ffd.poster.avif?t=1759308984\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236710/extras/5d988c72aa3ab92995f295a389808ffd.webm?t=1759308984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236710/extras/5d988c72aa3ab92995f295a389808ffd.mp4?t=1759308984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典三消角色扮演游戏再度回归！《Puzzle Quest: 不朽版》是 Puzzle Quest 系列的集大成之作，不仅为新时代玩家精心打磨，更完整收录了近 20 年来的所有经典内容。一次性体验原版《Puzzle Quest: Challenge of Warlords》、《Revenge of the Plague Lord》以及《The Legend Returns》的全部精彩内容！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Puzzle Quest: 不朽版》融合了经典的三消益智玩法与深度的角色扮演。匹配 3 颗或更多同色宝石获取法力，施展法术战胜强敌，收集物品与奖励，体验精彩剧情！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建可学习技能与法术的英雄</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三消战斗，面对不同敌人需采取不同策略</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游玩主线与支线任务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找助你一臂之力的同伴</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >学习法术，收集道具</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建成独属于你的城堡，兴建建筑可给予你特殊的能力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >捕获敌对生物，将其驯化为坐骑并训练他们</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >捕获怪物，游玩研究小游戏即可学习他们的法术</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发掘隐藏的符文，在城堡的熔炉中可创造魔法道具</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >于埃瑟利亚全境占领城市，扩展疆域</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236710/extras/c75bd7c41a7903054423f266880af41b.poster.avif?t=1759308984\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236710/extras/c75bd7c41a7903054423f266880af41b.webm?t=1759308984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236710/extras/c75bd7c41a7903054423f266880af41b.mp4?t=1759308984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好迎接挑战了吗？施展你的三消技巧，在拯救埃瑟利亚王国的征途中，与怪物和恶徒展开激战。</p>",
